            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Activation Rate = Activated Users / New Signups × 100. Activated means the user completed your defined activation event within a set window — usually 7, 14, or 30 days from signup. The event should predict long-term retention.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
