            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Onboarding is the sequence of steps that guides a new user. Activation is the outcome — the moment a user experiences core value. Onboarding is the mechanism; activation is the metric it moves.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
