              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Activation-rate changes show up in 2–4 weeks — as soon as one full activation window has elapsed for the new cohort. Downstream retention and revenue impact typically lands in 90 days.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

